&lt;h1 id="multidimensional-electrodynamic-pic"&gt;Multidimensional Electrodynamic PIC&lt;a class="anchor" href="#multidimensional-electrodynamic-pic"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
